{
  "stem": "13690.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were staying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did not know what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when-- this was at the daytime.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, let's say in the evening around 4, 5 o'clock, in January, the day is short-- the fighting started really.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The trenches, they started to open up the fire, one against the other.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the village that we were-- part of the village that we were in were just in between no man's land.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, in the one part was the Germans, in one part was the Russians.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were fighting, just one between the other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we-- and-- and those houses in that middle were just burning hell.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we could not stay in the barn, because there was no fireproof cellars.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was just simply it would blow up, like, in no time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we said to the peasant, 'We want to get out.' And we went out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we went walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that [? normal-- ?] falling, full of ammunition, you know, bullets, going, swishing to our heads.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we walked then into another village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that other village had already the Russians established, so to say-- it was the second line in command.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one of my cousins said, 'We are Jews.' So I said, 'Jews what?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no, no.' [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Starting to ?] say too much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't want to say anything, and we starting to be in that village.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you stayed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Was that village now free under the Russians?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was free under the Russians.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But still, they were-- they were skeptical, and they were reluctant to accept us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We spread.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We said, it's no good that we walk 10 people together, and we spread out in three groups again, how we would walk.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we did not say that we're Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
